g.text: European Union released an estimated 3230 MtCO2e in 2023 (excl. LULUCF), a change of -7.5 % compared to the previous year.
Per capita GHG emissions were 7.2 tCO2e in 2023. Cumulative CO2 emissions since 1850 were 301 GtCO2, or about 12% of global
emissions to date. Sources: EDGAR v9, GCB 2023, UNFCCC, Grassi et al. 2021
